          "description": "One of the only places where I feel like they actually listen to your problems and they\u2019re not rushing through your doctors appointment but somehow it\u2019s still able to be ready for the next patient at the perfect time. I will be truly trust testing my review today as I will be requesting something new so I will see if that attitude continues to be consistent.",
