          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIrSYXHLCu8mxyojGMO2j5t-zPvQxosl5e7l_diVfa4SiXw-wM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "My child waited to see Dr. Jayleecia Smith for over 3 hours. Her nor the two receptionists care about the patients time. They are very disrespectful, the workers sit around talking about other workers while using profanity, and respect the patients enough to talk a low tone so everyone don\u2019t hear about what\u2019s going on. No one addressed us to tell us how long the wait would be. They laughed at us when we told them we were here for so long and still did nothing. This should not be. They act like they are doing people a favor when they are getting paid for the job they\u2019re doing. Don\u2019t waste your time going to this facility unless you have a whole day to waste.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2twMmFEVnFWVFo0UnpoNFYyOHpYMkpOZVZOV1ptYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x9fd334e571b20b2!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOkp2aDVqVTZ4Rzh4V28zX2JNeVNWZmc%7C%7C?hl=en",
