          "description": "Family Health Institute is truly exceptional! From the moment I walked in, I felt welcomed and cared for. The staff is professional, kind, and attentive to every detail, and they genuinely take the time to listen and understand your needs. The doctors and nurses are knowledgeable, compassionate, and make you feel like more than just a patient\u2014they treat you like family. The environment is clean, organized, and comforting, which makes the whole experience stress-free. I\u2019m beyond grateful for the level of care and support I\u2019ve received here, and I highly recommend Family Health Institute to anyone looking for quality healthcare with a personal touch.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kWFVqbHZkemx0VmtzelVFNUNjVkI2UW1saFdrRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x9fd334e571b20b2!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOndXUjlvdzltVkszUE5CcVB6QmlhWkE%7C%7C?hl=en",
