          "description": "Please be aware that if you receive any medication that needs to be delivered to the clinic, you will have to come more than once for the same reason, as something always seems to come up. Communication between the clinic and your medication provider is terrible. Apparently, an unknown person, whom they refer to as \"someone,\" called the medication provider to request that my medication be sent to another of their clinics a second time. I asked who it was, but received no response. Someone they can't identify has my personal information and is calling the medication provider to change the delivery address for my medication a second time. I wonder what kind of information this unknown person has access to.",
